## Build / Test / Lint

Copy-paste these commands. All tools are managed by mise — no manual installs.

```sh
# First-time setup
mise install && uv sync

# Verify everything is correct (ground truth — exit 0 = done)
just verify

# Run linters only
just lint

# Auto-format Python and JS/TS
just format

# Drop into the mise-managed project shell
just shell
```

`just verify` is the canonical definition of "done". Before marking any task complete,
run `just verify` and confirm it exits 0. No exceptions.

