## Code Style

- **Python**: Ruff defaults from `pyproject.toml`. Line length 100. 4-space indent.
- **JS/TS** (when present): Biome defaults. 2-space indent. 100-char line length.
- **YAML/JSON/TOML/Markdown**: 2-space indent. LF line endings. UTF-8.
- All style rules are enforced by pre-commit hooks — run `just lint` before committing.
- Match existing patterns in the codebase. Do not introduce new libraries without checking
  `pyproject.toml` and `uv.lock` first.

