## Project Structure

```
harness/          — Python harness package (verify logic, core.py + cli.py + mcp_server.py)
tests/            — pytest test suite
.github/          — GitHub Actions workflows (ci.yml, deploy-smoke.yml)
pyproject.toml    — Python project config + uv dependency lock
justfile          — canonical task runner (just verify, lint, format, shell)
.mise.toml        — toolchain pin (Python 3.13+, Node 24+)
